        <h2>Available Checkout Pages</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <a href="/purchase">Purchase Flow</a>
            <p>Use this flow to handle one-time purchases using PayPal's card fields and buttons.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/vault">Vault Flow</a>
            <p>Use this flow to save card details for future transactions OR save PayPal payment source details during a one-time transaction for future transactions.</p>
